settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
Custom Shipping Info Snippet

Place this snippet below the Add to Cart button in your theme customiser by adding a "Custom Liquid Block"
Adjust the 'remaining_orders' variable in the Liquid code as needed
The shipping date is set to 3 days from now. To change this:

259200 is the number of seconds in 3 days (3 * 24 * 60 * 60)
For a different number of days, multiply the desired number of days by 86400 (seconds in a day)
For example, for 5 days use 432000 (5 * 86400)
{% endcomment %}



{% comment %}EDIT: Change the number of remaining orders here{% endcomment %}
{% assign remaining_orders = 16 %}
<div class="custom-shipping-info">
  <div class="shipping-info">
    <div class="info-column">
      <span class="pulsating-dot"></span>
      {% comment %}EDIT: Adjust the shipping date calculation here if needed{% endcomment %}
      <span class="shipping-text">Ships by <strong>{{ 'now' | date: '%s' | plus: 259200 | date: '%a, %b %d' }}</strong></span>
    </div>
    <div class="info-column">
      <span class="rotating-hourglass">‚è≥</span>
      <span class="orders-remaining"><strong>{{ remaining_orders }} orders</strong> at this price remaining</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  {% comment %}EDIT: Customize styles below{% endcomment %}
  .custom-shipping-info {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-family: sans-serif;
  }
  .shipping-info {
    background-color: #f5f5dc;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: #000;
    letter-spacing: normal;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .info-column {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    width: 48%; /* Adjust as needed */
  }
  .pulsating-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-right: 10px;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  .rotating-hourglass {
    animation: rotate 2s linear infinite;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 0.7; }
    100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes rotate {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }
</style>
